data.description: *****VA ASSUMPTION VA ASSUMPTION******* You should buy this home for the VA Assumption if NOTHING else at the low...low...lowwwww rate of 2.75%. Excellent Opportunity as a personal home or an investment opportunity. Move in ready meticulously renovated from head to toe! From the moment you walk in, you will be impressed with the diagonal coffered ceiling in the living room & the open floor plan. This gem has so much to offer, reach-in closet in primary bedroom with sliding barn doors that you'll love! A kitchen that walks out onto a raised deck and beautiful granite counter tops complemented by dark cabinetry. Fully finished walk-out basement offers more square footage and features two additional non-conforming bedrooms, brand new carpet, a family room, laundry area and a second 3/4 bathroom (peak behind the door to see the fully tiled shower). Just minutes from Blackstone, Midtown, shopping, hospitals, entertainment and easy access to I-480. AMA. Back yard is fully seeded and growing.
